{"word":"ἐμβιβάζω","slug":"ἐμβιβάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐμβιβάζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a>, βιβάζω</el> ‘cause to go’; ‘set/put in’] (causal of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐμβαίνω\">ἐμβαίνω</a></el>) in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only as maritime expression <b>cause to embark, put on board <a href='B:510 27:6'>Ac 27:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐμβῆναι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐμβλέπω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}